Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Victoria Gardens
Description: An outside shopping district that is popular for its rich history and beautiful architecture.

Name: Santa Monica Pier
Description: A pier filled with concession stands and a small amusement park. It is bright at night and very lively!

Name: Claremont Village
Description: An old downtown area in Claremont that has historical buildings and a variety of shops to browse and explore.

Name: The Lewis Library and Technology Center
Description: A great place to study, relax, and read some books. There are always big events that encourage patrons to check out books and be apart of the community.

Name: Little Tokyo
Description: A shopping district with a focus in Japanese stores and restaurants. It has very authentic and tasty meals that I want to have again some time soon.
